  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK846">
<l>aṟṟa maṟaittalō pullaṟivu tamvayiṟ</l>
<l>kuṟṟa maṟaiyā vaḻi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even to cover one's nakedness would be folly, if (one's) faults were not covered (by forsaking them).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
